  ],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "The bill requires a child care center to disclose the following information in its policies and procedures to the parents or guardians of children being served at the child care center:A statement that child care center workers are mandatory reporters of child abuse or neglect under state law; andFor a child care center that utilizes video recording equipment, a written disclosure of the presence of video recording equipment and the child care center's policies and procedures regarding the use of the video recording equipment and the generated video footage.(Note: This summary applies to this bill as introduced.)"
    }
  ],
